except one man has any woman been given the opportunity to have a box? I
have requested one for a  long time now and even offered to pay you.

But if you just send me the schematics I will build it, I am studying
electronics now and here in Mexico the random would be a good thing I
believe. Because even though  there&#39;s no English speaking stations near me
all I get is English J

Laura

